This file is intended for a network topology diagram.

Recommended structure to draw in diagrams.net (draw.io):

- Internet Cloud
   ↓
- Router (MikroTik / ISP Router)
   ↓
- Firewall (optional layer)
   ↓
- Core Switch (Cisco)
   ↓
-----------------------------
|            |             |
PCs       Server       Access Points
